oai_dc:dc.dc:title: TMR Test Mix
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Nelson, Arden
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: effective fiber
TMR mixers
nutrition management
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Displaced abomasums? Acidosis-laminitis? Butterfat depression? Any of the above plus high feed bills? Maybe the cows suffer from too little effective fiber and cannot perform like they are expected to. TMR mixers have been a tremendous tool for dairy nutrition management.
